<h2 id="how-do-i-get-involved">How Do I Get Involved?</h2>

<h3 id="donations">Donations</h3>

<p>If you enjoy using Vocal I would encourage you to consider a donation. Vocal is entirely open source and 100% free to download, and always will be, but it takes a surprising amount of money to create free software. Any donation, even $1, makes a big difference.</p>

<h3 id="translations">Translations</h3>
<p>If you are bilingual, translations are fantastic way to get involved. Just <a href="http://translations.launchpad.net/vocal">visit the Launchpad Translations page for Vocal</a> to get started.</p>

<h3 id="bug-reports">Bug Reports</h3>
<p>If you run into any bugs, have would like to suggest an improvement or new feature, <a href="http://bugs.launchpad.net/vocal">please report that here at Vocalâ€™s bug tracker on Launchpad.</a></p>

